如，-perfect-clear-magsafe-with-clicklock-iphone-15-cases&amp;amp;subid1=vergeroundupdeals031324&quot;>;Presidio Perfect-Clear&lt;/a>; 保护壳。它们具有 MagSafe 磁铁和抗菌保护，每件低至 39.99 美元（优惠 10 美元）...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/13/24099409/ Speck-cases-fitbit-ace-3-sling-tv-orange-amazon-fire-tv-omni-sale-deal&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/13/24099409/speck-cases-fitbit-ace-3-sling-tv-orange-amazon-fire-tv-omni-sale-deal" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/13/24099409/speck-cases-fitbit-ace-3-sling-tv-orange-amazon-fire-tv-omni-sale-deal</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-03-13T12:33:50-04:00</published><updated> 2024-03-13T12:33:50-04:00</updated><title> Block 的新加密钱包只能用真实现金购买</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 Block 的 Bitkey 加密钱包的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7KhTbjmoDiNABBk38T3iECzwPkk=/245x0:2264x1346/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73204210/bitkey_wallet.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Block&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;mgMqHB&quot;>;Jack Dorsey 领导的支付公司 Block 已发布其长期开发的比特币硬件钱包——但你不能使用加密货币购买它。您只能使用信用卡或借记卡购买 150 美元的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://bitkey.world/en-US/products/bitkey&quot;>;Bitkey 钱包&lt;/a>;，这表明加密货币可能并不那么流行正如其设计者所预期的那样。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;TSfxVL&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2022/4/6/23013420/jack-dorsey-block-hardware-crypto -wallet-bitcoin-rock-preview&quot;>;Block 于 2022 年首次推出了钱包原型&lt;/a>;，并于去年 12 月开放预订。自我托管比特币钱包，Dorsey &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/jack/status/1511738445399527427?s=20&quot;>;昵称&lt;/a>;“rockey”，允许用户在交易所之外存储加密货币保护资金免受潜在崩溃的影响。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;5dsCv8&quot;>;&lt;div style=&quot;left: 0; width: 100%; height: 0;position:relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; &quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;bD1iQf&quot;>;Bitkey 与移动应用程序和恢复工具配对，以防用户丢失钱包或手机。设备顶部有一个指纹传感器、一个 USB-C 充电端口...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/13/24099583/ block-crypto-wallet-bitkey-real-cash-purchase&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/13/24099583/block-crypto-wallet-bitkey-real-cash-purchase" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/13/24099583/block-crypto-wallet-bitkey-real-cash-purchase</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>